    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Customer Service Agent\n\nOwned By: Gary Safin\nLast Updated: 2026-07-03\n\nAn AI agent that answers customer questions by looking up \ninformation from multiple data sources.\n\n## Tools Available\n- Order Status: Look up order/delivery status by customer_id\n- Customer Info: Look up account/subscription details by customer_id\n- Product Info: Look up product features/pricing by product_name\n\n## Model\n- llama-3.3-70b-versatile\n\n## Usage\nChat with the agent via the Chat Trigger. Provide a customer ID \nwhen asking about orders or accounts.\n\nExample prompts:\n- \"I'm customer CUST-042. What's my order status?\"\n- \"What subscription is CUST-108 on?\"\n- \"Tell me about the Enterprise License\"\n\nPart of: n8n Foundations Program, N8N103 Course, Section 1",
        "height": 304,
        "width": 512
      },
